## â“ Problems?

### "Command not found"
Make sure you're in the project folder:
```bash
cd CredLink
```

### "Permission denied"
Make the script executable:
```bash
chmod +x start-simple.sh
```

### "Port already in use"
Kill existing processes:
```bash
lsof -ti:3001 | xargs kill -9
lsof -ti:8000 | xargs kill -9
```

Then run the script again.

